							-*-org-*-

* What is this

Here are all the files for the foswiki plugin part of the RainbruRPG's 
meta server.

* Dependencies

| *Module*               | *debian package*   | * Dependency*           |
|------------------------+--------------------+-------------------------|
| XML                    | libxml-libxml-perl | Mandatory               |
| DateTime               | libdatetime-perl   | Mandatory               |
| Test::Unit::Procedural | libtest-unit-perl  | Optional for Unit tests |
|                        |                    |                         |

* Installation

RainbrurpgMetaserverPlugin.txt is the documentation. It is installed 
in the /data/System directory

RainbrurpgMetaserverPlugin.pm is installed in the lib/Foswiki/Plugins/ dir.

The functions.pm file must be installed in a 
lib/Foswiki/Plugins/RainbrurpgMetaserverPlugin/ directory

Then, you need to enable it in the foswiki's configure script, using the 
'Extensions' tab.

* Usage

You can find online documentation in the System/RainbrurpgMetaserverPlugin
wiki page.
